<h1>融</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#cc7700;">róng</span><span class=alesi>(rong2)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 融 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 融</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/melt" style="color:black;">melt</a>, <a href="/dictionary/fuse" style="color:black;">fuse</a>; <a href="/dictionary/blend" style="color:black;">blend</a>, harmonize</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 16<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 16 strokes: <a href="/character/整" title="zheng3: orderly, neat, tidy; whole">整</a>, <a href="/character/器" title="qi4: receptacle, vessel; instrument">器</a>, <a href="/character/激" title="ji1: arouse, excite, incite; quickly">激</a>, <a href="/character/避" title="bi4: avoid; turn aside; escape; hide">避</a>, <a href="/character/嘴" title="zui3: mouth, lips">嘴</a>, <a href="/character/默" title="mo4: silent; quiet, still; dark">默</a>, <a href="/character/醒" title="xing3: wake up; sober up; startle">醒</a>, <a href="/character/操" title="cao1: conduct, run, control, manage">操</a>, <a href="/character/赞" title="zan4: help, support, assist, aid">赞</a>, <a href="/character/镜" title="jing4: mirror; lens; glass; glasses">镜</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/虫" title="Kangxi radical 142">虫</a>&nbsp;142.10</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 6 <br><small>Other HSK 6 characters: <a href="/character/债" title="zhai4: debt, loan, liabilities">债</a>, <a href="/character/侧" title="ce4: side; incline, slant, lean">侧</a>, <a href="/character/侠" title="xia2: chivalrous person; knight-errant">侠</a>, <a href="/character/纵" title="zong4: indulge in, give free reign to">纵</a>, <a href="/character/袭" title="xi2: raid, attack; inherit">袭</a>, <a href="/character/障" title="zhang4: separate; shield; barricade">障</a>, <a href="/character/讯" title="xun4: inquire; ask; examine; reproach">讯</a>, <a href="/character/涉" title="she4: ford stream, wade across">涉</a>, <a href="/character/刊" title="kan1: publication, periodical; publish">刊</a>, <a href="/character/爆" title="bao4: crackle, pop, burst, explode">爆</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-6" title="List of HSK 6 characters" style="white-spac