dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">螎|融[<span style="color:#cc7700;">róng</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- old variant of <a href="/dictionary/融">融</a>[rong2]<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><h2>Details</h2><p><b>Unicode code point:</b> U+878D</p></div>

